# HuggingFace Inference API token
# ----------------------------------
# Only required if running against the HuggingFace cloud fallback
# in dev (e.g. `npx expo start --web`). The production build uses
# the on-device Cactus runtime and does NOT need this token.
#
# To enable: `cp .env.example .env.local` and paste a token from
# https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
EXPO_PUBLIC_HF_API_KEY=
